import React from 'react'; import './Projects.css'; const Projects = () => { return (

Projects

  • Project One

    • Developed a responsive website using React and CSS.
    • Implemented authentication using Firebase.
    • Deployed the application on AWS.

  • Project Two

    • Created a mobile app using React Native.
    • Integrated with third-party APIs for data retrieval.
    • Used Redux for state management.

  • Project Three

    • Designed a single-page application with Vue.js.
    • Implemented real-time data updates using WebSockets.
    • Optimized performance for high-traffic use.

  • Project Four

    • Developed a chat application using Node.js and Socket.io.
    • Implemented user authentication and authorization.
    • Deployed on Heroku for public use.

  • Project Five

    • Built an e-commerce website using Django and React.
    • Integrated payment gateways for seamless transactions.
    • Implemented a comprehensive admin dashboard.

  • Project Six

    • Developed a task management tool using Angular.
    • Implemented drag-and-drop functionality for tasks.
    • Used Firebase for backend services.

  • Project Seven

    • Created a weather forecasting app using React and OpenWeatherMap API.
    • Implemented location-based weather updates.
    • Styled with Material-UI for a modern look.

  • Project Eight

    • Developed a personal finance tracker using Vue.js and Firebase.
    • Implemented data visualization with Chart.js.
    • Ensured mobile responsiveness with CSS Grid and Flexbox.

  • Project Nine

    • Created a blog platform using Ruby on Rails and React.
    • Implemented user authentication with Devise.
    • Deployed on AWS for scalability.
); } export default Projects;
